hopobject.body: What sort of music do you like? testosterone compound injection genesis This mug shot of Phil Spector was released after the music producer was convicted on April 13, 2009 of murder in the 2003 killing of Hollywood actress Lana Clarkson in 2003. He will likely spend the rest of his life in prison. Spector was once revered for revolutionizing pop music in the 1960s with his layered "Wall of Sound" production technique and now faces 18 years to life behind bars when he is sentenced on May 29.
